	they or their accessors are marked deprecated. (Affects
	Gtk.Entry.Editable, Gtk.FontSelection.Font,
	Gtk.Notebook.*TabBorder, Gtk.Object.UserData, and a bunch of old
	Gtk.ProgressBar properties).

