	* gdk/Drawable.custom:
	* sources/Gdk.metadata:
	* api/gdk-api.xml: Apply a modified version of a patch from
	Artemis <artemis@yandex.ru>, to fix and clean DrawPolygon and 
	DrawLines in Gdk.Drawable.

